      "author": "davidgolding",
      "description": "- **Core Command Interception**: Intercepts Obsidian's native `editor:toggle-bold`, `editor:toggle-italics`, etc., to correctly target whichever Tiptap editor (Main, Footnote, or Comment) is currently focused.\r\n- **Native OS Menu Support**: Added `beforeinput` event listeners to all editor instances. This allows the native `Format` menu to work correctly by mapping native browser input events directly to Tiptap commands.\r\n- **Robust Focus Tracking**: Implemented a global tracker in `src/main.js` that stays synchronized to clicks between the main manuscript and the sidebars.",
